User stories: 

Week 1:
1. As a gamer I want to play snake on raspberry pi so that I can have fun.
2. As a student I want to play fun games on raspberry pi so that I can learn about it in a fun way.
3. As a person who is interested in computing I want to do something fun on a raspberry pi so that I can learn about computers.

Week 2:

1. As a gamer I want to have scores in the snake game so that I am motivated more to play.
2. As a beginner gamer I want the game to say if I won or lost so that I can figure out what is going on.
3. As a gamer I want to have more games to play so that I won't get bored.
